              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Paradox of Duality grants Aun&apos;Va and his Honour Guards an increased Toughness characteristic (the unmodified value is used for the purposes of Instant Death), and a 4+ Cover Save, which may be re-rolled if it is failed.</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
