                          <characteristics>
                            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">From the second turn onwards, as long as the bearer is on the table at the beginning of the turn in which this device is being use, a single unit that is being held in Reserve may be deployed on a roll of 2+, though no other units in Reserve may be deployed this turn.</characteristic>
